raw_text = "~ start
do Story.set_location(\"mabels_room\")
if Story.mabel_desire > 0:
	Mabel: delete: img: mabel/75
	Mabel: Thought: I FORGOT TO WEAR MY SHIRT
	Mabel: Whoops, bad angle 😅 Hope you didn't see that 
	Mabel: Here's a better one 👀
Mabel: img: mabel/76
Mabel: What do you think hehe
Player: Whoa!
Player: Looking fancy today!
Mabel: Am I?
Mabel: Trying to look a bit smarter today for a change 🤓
Mabel: Mom's boxes of clothes are literally never ending 😂
Mabel: So... I'm just experimenting a little 😇
Mabel: Is it too formal?
- I think it's perfect [#trust]
	set Story.mabel_trust += 1
	Player: I think it's perfect!
	Mabel: Awwh really?
	Mabel: Maybe the nerd look is perfect for me afterall lol
- Maybe just a little [#lust]
	set Story.mabel_desire += 1
	Player: Maybe just a little
	Player: But suits you
	Mabel: I was thinking the same 
Mabel: I'm taking a page out of Naomi's style hehe
Mabel: 😊
Player: Awwh
Mabel: I'm packing my books for my class 🤓
Mabel: Whatcha doing?
Player: Quick breakfast!
Mabel: I don't know if this is weird to bring up buuut
Mabel: I feel like a grown up already!
Mabel: Just living alone, making my own breakfast, laundry on the weekends, studying in the evening
Mabel: And nobody to tell me to do these things
Player: Yeah, same here
Player: Sometimes it's a lot of work lol
Mabel: Yeah! Totally
do social_post(\"erika_sunbathing\")
Mabel: I feel like there's a lot of adulting left to do 👀
Mabel: Other girls look like they've already figured it out tbh 👉👈
Mabel: Thought: Maybe we could do something... like that eventually I mean... No rush
Player: What do you mean?
Mabel: Nothing, just getting ahead of myself 😇
Player: Still missing home?
if Story.mabel_trust >= 50:
	Mabel: I don't!
	Player: Wow, didn't expect that!
	Mabel: Ask me why silly 😉
	Player: Why?? 😄
	Mabel: Because I have you with me 🥰
	Mabel: I've been feeling safe and protected with you around
	Mabel: I know you live a bit far but still
	Mabel: Somehow I know you're right around the corner when I need you to be 🩷
	Mabel: 🫶
	Player: Awwh
	Player: 🫶
else:
	Mabel: I do but
	Mabel: In a different way now
	Mabel: I feel like... the Mabel that left home isn't the same one that's going to return home one day
	Player: Wow, that sounds sad!
	Mabel: Is it? 
	Mabel: In a way I guess
	Mabel: But I don't know, it doesn't scare me as much as it should
	Mabel: I'll be more of a lady and less a girl 💅🤭
	Player: A lovely lady 😁
	Mabel: 🤭
Mabel: Alright packing done!
Mabel: Gotta go
=> END
"
metadata/dialogue_manager_version = "3.7.1"
